Pal/Sk sword and shield of eternal duty<br>
Sword 1hs dam 50 delay 40 bonus 5 fire bonus 5 cold bonus 5 AC 50 hp 100 mana 100 36% haste<br>
<br>
shield AC 100 +40 bonus dam to bash  damage avoidence 10% +100hp +100mana + 30 to all saves.  flowing thought 3.<br>
<br>
