<br>
Int casters a back item +40 int, +200 mana +20 to all saves, FT3, extended range 3,  <br>
<br>
war weapon of 15/20, fb bonus 2, cold base bonus 2, +50 ac, +20 to all stats + 20 to all saves. plus a proc which increases hate list points by 50 and does 100dd.<br>
<br>
ranger, rogue, monk, beast lord, chest plate of 80ac +40% haste +25 to dex/stam/agi/str right click evac to zone line.<br>
<br>
bards a musical instrument of versitility.  Acts as type of instrument for song you sing.  Adds 20% range and increase of 70% durration.  + 20 to all saves.  +50 to charisma.<br>
<br>
<br>
